319
00:18:33,460 --> 00:18:34,760
It just isn't meant to be.

320
00:18:35,660 --> 00:18:36,760
Who will pity me?

321
00:18:37,340 --> 00:18:38,380
Let's not listen to it.

322
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:39,220
Not this song.

323
00:18:39,220 --> 00:18:40,180
How about

324
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:41,120
Autumn Wind Tune?

325
00:18:41,420 --> 00:18:43,320
If I knew it would be so heart-wrenching,

326
00:18:45,620 --> 00:18:47,400
I wouldn't have met you.

327
00:18:48,420 --> 00:18:50,240
If I hadn't met Zhao,

328
00:18:51,100 --> 00:18:53,080
