329
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:55,320
Not this song.

330
00:18:55,700 --> 00:18:57,880
Didn't you love listening
to the Roadside Mulberry?

331
00:18:58,140 --> 00:18:59,520
Let's listen to the Roadside Mulberry.

332
00:18:59,900 --> 00:19:01,320
Zhao has his own wife,

333
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:04,360
yet Guangde has no husband.

334
00:19:06,740 --> 00:19:09,320
In the end, it is a story of three people.

335
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:13,280
But I don't have a name in it.

336
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:15,320
Princess.

337
00:19:15,580 --> 00:19:16,720
Please stop crying.

338
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:19,280
What should I do?

339
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:22,080
With an endless stream of dreamy thoughts,

340
00:19:24,620 --> 00:19:26,080
