343
00:19:36,660 --> 00:19:39,480
Princess, you can't do this.

344
00:19:45,020 --> 00:19:46,360
Say it.

345
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:52,160
Guangde trapped herself in the palace,

346
00:19:52,620 --> 00:19:54,240
not eating or drinking all day.

347
00:19:54,860 --> 00:19:56,820
No matter how I persuade her, it's useless.

348
00:19:56,820 --> 00:19:58,460
Your Majesty and I

349
00:19:58,460 --> 00:19:59,640
watched her grow up.

350
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:01,800
She has been spoiled since little.

351
00:20:02,580 --> 00:20:03,500
Now

352
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:05,240
she finally has someone she likes.

353
00:20:05,460 --> 00:20:07,280
But trapped in love,

354
00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:10,160
she's been crying all day.

355
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:11,800
It really hurts

356
00:20:12,340 --> 00:20:14,720
to see her like this.

357
00:20:16,420 --> 00:20:17,660
Marriages

358
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:19,000
are arranged by parents.

359
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:20,880
Your Majesty, why don't you

360
00:20:21,340 --> 00:20:22,800
grant Guangde a marriage?

361
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:26,120
Isn't that using power to force him?

362
00:20:26,340 --> 00:20:27,560
I think

363
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:29,640
it also depends on timing.

364
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:30,980
Now

365
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:33,400
the eligible candidates

366
00:20:33,740 --> 00:20:36,160
are only Changsheng and Guangde.

367
00:20:36,580 --> 00:20:38,180
I've always

368
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:39,520
been worrying.

369
00:20:39,860 --> 00:20:41,280
I just can't

370
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:44,080
stop worrying.

371
00:20:44,420 --> 00:20:45,980
What if Guangde is selected?

372
00:20:45,980 --> 00:20:47,640
It's such a far place.

373
00:20:48,340 --> 00:20:50,620
I will never

374
00:20:50,620 --> 00:20:52,840
stop worrying then.

375
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:56,320
Okay, okay, don't cry.

376
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:01,080
Forget it.

377
00:21:01,820 --> 00:21:02,660
Gao An.

378
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:04,740
Yes.

379
00:21:05,220 --> 00:21:07,560
Get Zhao Huaibi here.

380
00:21:07,900 --> 00:21:08,740
Yes.

381
00:21:12,540 --> 00:21:14,660
(Imperial Study)

382
00:21:14,660 --> 00:21:15,600
Yuzhi.

383
00:21:15,820 --> 00:21:17,160
(Waves by the Sea)
I remember

384
00:21:17,580 --> 00:21:19,320
