385
00:21:20,940 --> 00:21:22,240
- Yes.
- Yuzhi.

386
00:21:22,580 --> 00:21:24,080
You are young and promising.

387
00:21:24,460 --> 00:21:26,580
You're my capable assistant

388
00:21:26,580 --> 00:21:27,620
and an incredible general

389
00:21:27,620 --> 00:21:29,320
in Fuyu.

390
00:21:29,860 --> 00:21:31,080
It's just

391
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:34,840
at this age, there is no one
to take care of you.

392
00:21:35,420 --> 00:21:38,560
I'm really worried.

393
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:40,740
Unify the family first

394
00:21:40,740 --> 00:21:43,000
and then can you pacify the world.

395
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:46,980
Last time I mentioned

396
00:21:46,980 --> 00:21:49,660
Princess Guangde's marriage to you.

397
00:21:49,660 --> 00:21:50,500
Your Majesty.

398
00:21:51,180 --> 00:21:52,020
I...

399
00:21:55,660 --> 00:21:56,800
I have decided

400
00:21:57,820 --> 00:21:59,280
to marry Princess Changsheng.

401
00:22:06,980 --> 00:22:08,600
This is so sudden.

402
00:22:09,660 --> 00:22:10,560
Yuzhi.

403
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:12,560
I think you

404
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:14,100
