408
00:22:17,660 --> 00:22:18,500
Let's give it some time.

409
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:24,260
Jin.

410
00:22:24,260 --> 00:22:25,280
You came.

411
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:26,500
What's wrong?

412
00:22:26,740 --> 00:22:28,420
