413
00:22:28,420 --> 00:22:30,720
Changsheng has been acting
a little weird towards me lately.

414
00:22:31,580 --> 00:22:32,420
You had a fight?

415
00:22:32,420 --> 00:22:33,340
No.

416
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:34,800
Changsheng and I didn't fight.

417
00:22:35,620 --> 00:22:36,940
But that feeling

418
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:38,800
is worse than we had a fight.

419
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:40,740
You guys have a close relationship.

420
00:22:40,740 --> 00:22:42,620
And you haven't had any fights,
so it should be fine.

421
00:22:42,620 --> 00:22:43,460
Yes.

422
00:22:43,940 --> 00:22:45,940
My brother helped Guangde come up with ideas,

423
00:22:45,940 --> 00:22:47,320
and I tipped them off.

424
00:22:47,820 --> 00:22:49,240
But since I tipped them off,

425
00:22:49,620 --> 00:22:51,320
Changsheng has been even more strange to me.

426
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:53,020
Doesn't Zilv

427
00:22:53,020 --> 00:22:54,360
like Her Highness?

428
00:22:54,940 --> 00:22:56,320
Why is he helping Princess Guangde?

429
00:22:58,860 --> 00:23:00,940
Because my brother

430
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:02,240
really likes Changsheng.

431
00:23:02,940 --> 00:23:04,880
But Changsheng doesn't want to marry him.

432
00:23:04,940 --> 00:23:06,460
(Respect and Prudence)

433
00:23:06,460 --> 00:23:08,260
So my brother secretly opposed it

434
00:23:08,260 --> 00:23:09,600
and leaves Changsheng with no choice.

435
00:23:09,940 --> 00:23:11,320
Then she'll marry into our family.

436
00:23:13,740 --> 00:23:15,180
Xiao can't do this.

437
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:17,080
My brother has broken a leg.

438
00:23:17,660 --> 00:23:19,240
If it's true as the rumor says,

439
00:23:19,460 --> 00:23:20,840
then after marrying Changsheng,

440
00:23:21,220 --> 00:23:22,120
my brother will...

441
00:23:22,380 --> 00:23:24,180
I think now I know the problem

442
00:23:24,180 --> 00:23:25,040
between you two.

443
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:26,020
What's it?

444
00:23:26,020 --> 00:23:26,860
You

445
00:23:26,860 --> 00:23:27,940
are smart,

446
00:23:27,940 --> 00:23:29,000
but have a fool in your sleeve.

447
00:23:29,380 --> 00:23:30,660
What does it mean?

448
00:23:30,660 --> 00:23:31,500
Let me ask you.

449
00:23:31,700 --> 00:23:32,820
You tipped them off

450
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:34,380
to help Changsheng

451
00:23:34,380 --> 00:23:35,580
or you're afraid that

452
00:23:35,580 --> 00:23:36,760
Changsheng will marry your brother?

453
00:23:37,380 --> 00:23:38,220
I...

454
00:23:40,580 --> 00:23:41,420
I...

455
00:23:42,660 --> 00:23:44,240
If I really can't get married,

456
00:23:44,860 --> 00:23:46,080
I'll marry your brother.

457
00:23:46,340 --> 00:23:48,240
Anyway, he has already broken a leg.

458
00:23:48,620 --> 00:23:49,940
There shouldn't be any more problems.

459
00:23:49,940 --> 00:23:51,760
You can't marry my brother.

460
00:23:52,820 --> 00:23:53,660
Well,

461
00:23:54,460 --> 00:23:55,340
my brother

462
00:23:55,340 --> 00:23:57,160
is actually an embroidered pillow,

463
00:23:57,500 --> 00:23:58,560
pleasant to the eye but of no use.

464
00:23:58,940 --> 00:24:00,080
Usually, he looks

465
00:24:00,340 --> 00:24:01,940
elegant on the outside,

466
00:24:01,940 --> 00:24:02,900
but he's terrible

467
00:24:02,900 --> 00:24:03,740
behind people's backs.

468
00:24:04,140 --> 00:24:05,760
You don't know, Changsheng.

469
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:07,880
How could I not know?

470
00:24:08,580 --> 00:24:09,480
Don't worry.

471
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:11,460
I won't choose

472
00:24:11,460 --> 00:24:12,800
Xiao Zilv to be my husband.

473
00:24:13,500 --> 00:24:15,180
Even if I have to marry into Great Tang,

474
00:24:15,180 --> 00:24:16,240
I won't consider him.

475
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:20,000
I'm going to apologize to Changsheng.

476
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:22,620
Young Lady, Princess Changsheng is here.

477
00:24:22,620 --> 00:24:24,220
Changsheng? Let her in.

478
00:24:24,220 --> 00:24:25,080
Yes, Young Lady.

479
00:24:34,100 --> 00:24:34,940
Jin.

480
00:24:37,260 --> 00:24:38,600
Last time you left in a hurry,

481
00:24:38,860 --> 00:24:40,560
and didn't even take
the fruit I prepared for you.

482
00:24:41,180 --> 00:24:42,640
Today I feel better,

483
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:44,040
so I brought it to you.

484
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:49,660
This fruit

485
00:24:49,660 --> 00:24:51,040
is from another country.

486
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:58,660
It may not look pretty,

487
00:24:58,660 --> 00:25:00,120
but it tastes very sweet.

488
00:25:07,580 --> 00:25:08,860
You're going to be a bride.

489
00:25:08,860 --> 00:25:09,960
It's a happy event.

490
00:25:10,620 --> 00:25:12,140
Do you know how many people
want to get married

491
00:25:12,140 --> 00:25:13,280
but can't get married?

492
00:25:14,380 --> 00:25:15,240
Changsheng.

493
00:25:16,580 --> 00:25:17,480
Sorry.

494
00:25:20,140 --> 00:25:21,260
Between you and me,

495
00:25:21,260 --> 00:25:22,420
this is the last word

496
00:25:22,420 --> 00:25:23,320
I want to hear.

497
00:25:24,180 --> 00:25:25,800
You have always treated me as a close friend.

498
00:25:26,340 --> 00:25:27,320
But I only helped you

499
00:25:27,820 --> 00:25:29,720
because of my own selfish intentions.

500
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:31,520
I don't deserve it.

501
00:25:32,380 --> 00:25:33,560
What are you talking about?

502
00:25:33,940 --> 00:25:35,160
You helped me.

503
00:25:35,380 --> 00:25:36,500
Isn't it that you just hope

504
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:38,360
I can marry someone I like?

505
00:25:38,940 --> 00:25:39,880
I'm afraid

506
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:41,800
you'll marry my brother.

507
00:25:43,020 --> 00:25:44,260
Fool.

508
00:25:44,260 --> 00:25:46,000
I didn't want to marry your brother.

509
00:25:48,860 --> 00:25:49,940
Actually, my brother

510
00:25:49,940 --> 00:25:51,400
really likes you.

511
00:25:51,820 --> 00:25:53,280
He is just too embarrassed to speak up.

512
00:25:53,740 --> 00:25:55,080
He was rejected by you before,

513
00:25:55,210 --> 00:25:56,540
so he thought of ways

514
00:25:56,540 --> 00:25:57,720
to ruin your dates.

515
00:26:01,940 --> 00:26:03,040
Between men and women,

516
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:04,560
there's not just about love

517
00:26:05,380 --> 00:26:06,480
but also friendship.

518
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:07,780
He's

519
00:26:08,140 --> 00:26:09,560
just a friend to me.

520
00:26:10,980 --> 00:26:12,840
It's impossible between us.

521
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:18,220
Fortunately, General Zhao chose you.

522
00:26:18,220 --> 00:26:19,220
