523
00:26:19,220 --> 00:26:20,320
He shouldn't be afraid.

524
00:26:20,620 --> 00:26:21,640
Don't say that.

525
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:23,480
My bad. My bad.

526
00:26:24,740 --> 00:26:26,800
Your hair is so pretty.

527
00:26:27,820 --> 00:26:28,800
