530
00:26:33,420 --> 00:26:34,320
Changsheng.

531
00:26:37,620 --> 00:26:39,560
This is the wedding gift I prepared for you.

532
00:26:40,420 --> 00:26:41,580
I wish you and Xie Lin

533
00:26:41,580 --> 00:26:42,520
