00:27:54,380 --> 00:27:55,220
How bold!

538
00:27:58,880 --> 00:27:59,920
Your Highness, please forgive me.

539
00:28:00,220 --> 00:28:01,520
I didn't know you were coming.

540
00:28:01,820 --> 00:28:02,800
The servants

541
00:28:03,220 --> 00:28:04,500
