542
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:05,500
Don't blame them.

543
00:28:05,500 --> 00:28:06,480
I didn't allow them to say it.

544
00:28:11,940 --> 00:28:12,780
This charcoal

545
00:28:13,420 --> 00:28:14,320
burns really well.

546
00:28:15,420 --> 00:28:16,260
Sit down.

547
00:28:20,620 --> 00:28:21,720
This security bracelet

548
00:28:22,380 --> 00:28:24,000
was given to you by Guangde.

549
00:28:24,900 --> 00:28:25,740
Yes.

550
00:28:32,460 --> 00:28:33,880
You said you wanted to marry me.

551
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:35,260
Do you still mean it?

552
00:28:35,940 --> 00:28:36,940
I make a deal,

553
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:37,960
I keep a deal.

554
00:28:45,580 --> 00:28:46,720
Then are you marrying me

555
00:28:48,260 --> 00:28:49,400
just to honor the promise

556
00:28:50,460 --> 00:28:51,800
or that you really like me?

557
00:28:56,260 --> 00:28:57,100
Your Highness.

558
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:09,060
Your Highness.

559
00:29:09,220 --> 00:29:11,080
What are you doing?

560
00:29:22,090 --> 00:29:23,130
Your Highness, please forgive me.

561
00:29:23,620 --> 00:29:24,600
Sorry for the offense.

562
00:29:29,100 --> 00:29:30,320
I didn't plan to throw it away.

563
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:32,000
Since it is a precious thing,

564
00:29:32,380 --> 00:29:33,880
you should treasure it.

565
00:29:37,020 --> 00:29:38,080
Guangde is waiting for you.

566
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:40,340
Without you,

567
00:29:40,940 --> 00:29:41,960
she will really die.

568
00:29:42,940 --> 00:29:44,700
You fight on the battlefield

569
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:46,480
just to protect the ones you love.

570
00:29:50,500 --> 00:29:51,900
If Guangde died,

571
00:29:51,900 --> 00:29:53,080
would you really be happy?

572
00:30:00,020 --> 00:30:01,520
Listen to the voice in your heart.

573
00:30:03,860 --> 00:30:04,700
But...

574
00:30:05,380 --> 00:30:06,360
But Your Highness, you...

575
00:30:08,340 --> 00:30:09,260
Mr. Envoy

576
00:30:09,260 --> 00:30:10,700
is discussing the marriage with His Majesty

577
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:12,040
in the Imperial Study.

578
00:30:12,980 --> 00:30:13,820
Go now.

579
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,080
Thank you, Your Highness.

580
00:30:35,940 --> 00:30:37,520
(It's obviously a story for three people.)

581
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:39,500
(Guangde,)

582
00:30:40,420 --> 00:30:42,320
(I am the one who should not have a name.)

583
00:30:48,100 --> 00:30:49,180
Mr. Envoy

584
00:30:49,180 --> 00:30:51,220
