587
00:30:57,180 --> 00:30:58,380
Among the women of appropriate age

588
00:30:58,380 --> 00:30:59,560
in Shangkang City,

589
00:30:59,900 --> 00:31:01,740
Princess Changsheng and Princess Guangde

590
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:02,840
are both excellent candidates.

591
00:31:03,660 --> 00:31:04,560
I don't know which

592
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,080
will Your Majesty choose.

593
00:31:06,940 --> 00:31:08,320
I watched

594
00:31:08,820 --> 00:31:10,940
Changsheng grow up.

595
00:31:10,940 --> 00:31:12,500
She's dignified and virtuous,

596
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:14,140
endowed with civil and martial virtues.

597
00:31:14,140 --> 00:31:16,480
To be honest, I'm really reluctant

598
00:31:16,860 --> 00:31:18,840
to marry her to Great Tang.

599
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:20,880
Since you're reluctant,

600
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:22,800
then I choose Princess Guangde

601
00:31:23,220 --> 00:31:24,520
for Prince Qin.

602
00:31:25,420 --> 00:31:26,260
Guangde...

603
00:31:27,940 --> 00:31:29,660
Guangde is naughty by nature.

604
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:30,760
She isn't a good choice.

605
00:31:31,980 --> 00:31:32,940
I think

606
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:34,600
Princess Guangde is unrestrained,

607
00:31:34,820 --> 00:31:36,020
innocent and lively.

608
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:37,500
Besides, I've heard before

609
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:38,800
she made a bet with Her Highness

610
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:41,420
that if she failed to choose a husband

611
00:31:41,420 --> 00:31:43,080
before I leave,

612
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:45,000
she'll willingly go
for the peace-making marriage.

613
00:31:45,460 --> 00:31:47,320
Now General Zhao has made a choice.

614
00:31:47,800 --> 00:31:48,660
I am afraid...

615
00:31:48,660 --> 00:31:49,640
Your Majesty.

616
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:51,420
General Zhao asks to see you.

617
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:52,260
I won't see him.

618
00:31:55,860 --> 00:31:57,500
Your Majesty, sorry for the rudeness.

619
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:58,360
I came

620
00:31:59,660 --> 00:32:01,000
to ask you to grant me a marriage.

621
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:02,580
Take him out.

622
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:05,580
Your Majesty.

623
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:07,980
Please

624
00:32:07,980 --> 00:32:10,320
marry Princess Guangde to me.

625
00:32:18,980 --> 00:32:20,600
General Zhao asked for permission

626
00:32:21,180 --> 00:32:23,500
to marry me?

627
00:32:23,500 --> 00:32:24,340
Yes.

628
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:26,840
How come?

629
00:32:27,860 --> 00:32:29,040
What?

630
00:32:29,700 --> 00:32:31,160
You don't like it?

631
00:32:31,620 --> 00:32:32,880
What happened?

632
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:34,880
Liu Changsheng, did you...

633
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,340
Yes.

634
00:32:36,340 --> 00:32:37,320
I'm incompetent,

635
00:32:37,660 --> 00:32:39,400
and can't keep General Zhao by my side.

636
00:32:39,660 --> 00:32:40,880
I am defeated.

637
00:32:41,660 --> 00:32:42,900
You are not generous.

638
00:32:42,900 --> 00:32:43,820
Your guest is here.

639
00:32:43,820 --> 00:32:45,040
Aren't you going to give me a cup of tea?

640
00:32:45,420 --> 00:32:46,320
Liu Changsheng.

641
00:32:46,580 --> 00:32:48,080
Do you think I can't afford to lose?

642
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:50,700
I don't need you to cheat.

643
00:32:50,700 --> 00:32:52,100
Father likes me so much.

644
00:32:52,100 --> 00:32:54,220
He won't want to marry me far away.

645
00:32:54,220 --> 00:32:55,940
You gave Zhao Huaibi to me,

646
00:32:55,940 --> 00:32:57,080
what will you do?

647
00:32:57,380 --> 00:32:59,320
The person General Zhao likes is you.

648
00:32:59,740 --> 00:33:01,160
I just granted his wish.

649
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:03,740
I...

650
00:33:03,740 --> 00:33:04,580
Don't cry.

651
00:33:05,380 --> 00:33:07,080
I like it when you argue with me.

652
00:33:08,140 --> 00:33:10,280
What did your storybooks say?

653
00:33:11,940 --> 00:33:13,560
Those love stories

654
00:33:13,980 --> 00:33:15,180
are not so amazing

655
00:33:15,180 --> 00:33:16,120
as they look.

656
00:33:16,460 --> 00:33:17,420
It's either

657
00:33:17,420 --> 00:33:18,600
quarrelsome lovers

658
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:20,640
or childhood sweethearts.

659
00:33:20,940 --> 00:33:22,180
First, the two people were at odds.

660
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:23,640
Then their fates entangle.

661
00:33:24,020 --> 00:33:25,460
If there's no fate,

662
00:33:25,460 --> 00:33:27,000
we can create opportunities ourselves.

663
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:28,120
Just pester him.

664
00:33:30,220 --> 00:33:31,940
I'll use these tips

665
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:33,520
to find my destined man.

666
00:33:34,860 --> 00:33:35,700
Changsheng.

667
00:33:36,660 --> 00:33:37,520
Thank you.

668
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:40,800
Alright.

669
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:43,560
I told you it's a convincing defeat.

670
00:33:44,660 --> 00:33:45,880
I didn't cheat.

671
00:33:47,140 --> 00:33:48,560
How could I let you win?

672
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:53,320
There's still flexibility

673
00:33:53,820 --> 00:33:55,120
on the peace-making marriage.

674
00:34:07,260 --> 00:34:11,340
(Prince Changle's Mansion)

675
00:34:18,380 --> 00:34:20,080
What's with the forced smile?

676
00:34:21,220 --> 00:34:23,060
You became soft-hearted

677
00:34:23,060 --> 00:34:23,900
at the last moment?

678
00:34:25,740 --> 00:34:27,160
There will be someone waiting for me.

679
00:34:27,740 --> 00:34:28,640
The smile is not forced.

680
00:34:32,140 --> 00:34:34,080
Want to know what I told His Majesty?

681
00:34:38,260 --> 00:34:39,100
No.

682
00:34:39,580 --> 00:34:41,560
Your words cannot be taken back.

683
00:34:42,420 --> 00:34:44,560
I have no control over my affairs.

684
00:34:46,420 --> 00:34:47,260
It's useless to talk more.

685
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:50,620
Up to you.

686
00:34:53,420 --> 00:34:54,440
I heard

687
00:34:54,740 --> 00:34:56,560
Great Tang is particularly rich.

688
00:34:59,100 --> 00:35:01,140
It's located in a remote place,

689
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:01,980
totally worthless.

690
00:35:02,100 --> 00:35:03,120
People there

691
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:04,720
are literate

692
00:35:04,720 --> 00:35:05,740
and doors are unbolted at night.

693
00:35:06,700 --> 00:35:07,540
Not at all.

694
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:09,300
The people there are all unruly

695
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,160
and they lie all the time.

696
00:35:10,160 --> 00:35:11,560
People's hearts are no longer what they were.

697
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:24,660
Zhaojun held the jade saddle
and embarked on the journey.

698
00:35:25,460 --> 00:35:27,560
Tears wetting her cheeks.

699
00:35:29,380 --> 00:35:31,040
Today, she is still a member of the Han Palace.

700
00:35:32,300 --> 00:35:34,360
Tomorrow, she will be the concubine
of a barbarian.

